      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in fair condition. The interior shows visible wear on upholstery and trim surfaces, with some staining and scuffing on high-contact areas. Controls and displays are functional, though there are minor cosmetic issues throughout the cabin. The exterior has noticeable scratches and surface blemishes. Mechanically the car runs, but it shows its age and use. Suitable for a buyer looking for a functional daily driver at a lower price point.",
      "price": 20000.0,
